{"questionId":"3908233","questionHtml":"<p>A mass is oscillating with simple harmonic motion. At time <em>t</em>, the acceleration is at a positive maximum.</p>\n<p>What are the displacement and velocity of the mass at time <em>t</em>?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"height:178px;border-color:#000000;width:387.8px;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:57px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width:147px;text-align:center;\"><strong>Displacement</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:158.8px;text-align:center;\"><strong>Velocity</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:57px;\">A.</td>\n<td style=\"width:147px;text-align:left;\">positive maximum</td>\n<td style=\"width:158.8px;text-align:left;\">zero</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:57px;\">B.</td>\n<td style=\"width:147px;text-align:left;\">negative maximum</td>\n<td style=\"width:158.8px;text-align:left;\">zero</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:57px;\">C.</td>\n<td style=\"width:147px;text-align:left;\">positive maximum</td>\n<td style=\"width:158.8px;text-align:left;\">negative maximum</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:57px;\">D.</td>\n<td style=\"width:147px;text-align:left;\">negative maximum</td>\n<td style=\"width:158.8px;text-align:left;\">negative maximum</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","markschemeHtml":"<p>B</p>","meta":{"questionId":"3908233","referenceCode":"23M.1A.SL.TZ2.13","subjectId":"59-dp-physics-first-assessment-2025","title":"A mass is oscillating with simple harmonic motion. At time t, the acceleration is at a positive maximum. What are the displacement and velocity of the mass at time t? Displacement ","paper":"1A","level":"SL","questionNumber":"13","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["C. Wave behaviour","C.1 Simple harmonic motion"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}